<lyrics>[V1]
 Nana moma I̱ki yokʋt,
 Ushi Chisʋs illi tok,
 Micha Shilombish aienʋt
 Chihowa achʋfa ka,
 Chu̱kʋsh a̱hli
 Isht il aiokpanchashke.</lyrics>
